{"tid":2385054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"GME風暴》記者質詢券商曾支付財長Yellen天價演講費　自宮發言人：冇問題","createTime":"2021-01-28T23:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T09:50:16.000Z","uid":35519,"like":91,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e390f1ab7c0925559b04bfc370249040b8ffb7","tid":2385054,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QtGWhF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QtGWhF.png&h=24959e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n財長耶倫（Janet Yellen）曾收取券商Citadel 810,000美元演講費，而Citadel與GME風眼券商Robinhood的母公司及沽空機構Melvin Capital Management有密切生意來往。<br />\n<br />\n記者質詢Yellen會否避席參與拜登內閣就Gamestop事件的討論及決定，自宮發言人表示他們一直密切關注事件，並表示耶倫享負盛名，值得在上任財長前收取天價演講費用。<br />\n<br />\n記者質詢片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/IsicaLynn/status/1354894529208348673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsicaLynn%2Fstatus%2F1354894529208348673&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1wyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=2af89417\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsicaLynn%2Fstatus%2F1354894529208348673&h=50299dd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/IsicaLynn/status/1354894529208348673</a>"},{"pid":"7633fab467a0024b8bc03c1e37cb54ac755389b4","tid":2385054,"uid":39221,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:26:38.000Z","msg":"咁快就浮哂上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de692f314fe68e112a41b5fe867b1d6c9749ece","tid":2385054,"uid":212632,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:27:28.000Z","msg":"呢單嘢有排爆"},{"pid":"75dde52926c4439c93b27db8e783e02344d1cde4","tid":2385054,"uid":4574,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:29:34.000Z","msg":"deep state <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c10efe8302db6eb4cbb77ae5ab2a986428b697b","tid":2385054,"uid":136311,"like":10